(509, 374, 'opis', '<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Adrian Winiarek</strong> is a Development Director at MDC<sup>2</sup> within the Southern Poland team. Most recently he was a development director at Panattoni Europe responsible for new developments in Southern Poland. Previously he held a position of business Development Manager in Goodman (GLP Europe). In his career Adrian has been involved in delivering new industrial facilities for leading International and Polish companies from various business sectors and developed more than 200 000 square meters of A-class buildings. Adrian graduated from the Warsaw School of Economics – faculty of Corporate Finance with specialization in real estate.</p>'),
