(543, 537, 'opis', '<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Andrzej Lasocki</strong> is a Development Director at MDC<sup>2</sup> . Most recently he was responsible for expanding GLP’s (GLP Europe) portfolio in key market locations across Poland. Andrzej has developed more than 15 warehouse projects in Poland, with a value exceeding €300 million. He has been connected with Polish real estate market for 20 years and he worked for the biggest commercial developers active in the country including: GLP, Goodman, Panattoni Europe, Echo Investment and Caelum Development. He has a proven track record in the development of more than 40 projects.</p>'),
