(845, 729, 'opis', '<p class=\"v1v1msonormal\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Izabela Ciżyńska</strong> is a Junior Development Manager at MDC<sup>2</sup>\'s Development team. Her responsibilities include a coordination of development and commercial processes within the team and the exchange of information with other departments. Izabela supports the work of business development directors by preparation of draft commercial materials, offers, calculations, reports, presentations and other major documents. She is also vital in commissioning design concepts and the cooperation with architects, lawyers, brokers and tenants.</p>\r\n<p class=\"v1v1msonormal\" style=\"text-align: left;\">She began her professional career as a land surveyor and gained her warehouse real estate experience working in Goodman Poland as an Administrative Assistant and then Property Manager looking after two assets in Lublin and Grodzisk Mazowiecki. Most recently she worked in Panattoni as Development Coordinator.</p>\r\n<p class=\"v1v1msonormal\" style=\"text-align: left;\">Izabela graduated from the Warsaw University of Technology – faculty of Geodesy and Cartography and Administration and Social Sciences as well as postgraduate studies of Property Management at the University of Social Sciences in Warsaw. She speaks fluent English and intermediate French and Turkish.</p>'),
