(999, 1076, 'opis', 'Łukasz is responsible for the development of logistics and industrial projects in Central and Northern Poland. He gained his professional experience working for key developers on the market, including Panattoni, Ghelamco and ORCO Property Group. He was responsible for the commercialization and development of several dozen development projects. He took part in over 60 leasing transactions with a total area of ​​over 460,000 sq m. serving tenants such as FedEx, InPost, Rohlig SUUS Logistics, Rhenus Logistics and FM Logistics.\r\nŁukasz is a graduate of the Faculty of Civil Engineering at the Warsaw University of Technology. He developed his management competences by completing the International MBA program at the Business School of the Warsaw University of Technology and the Jacek Santorski Academy of Leadership Psychology.'),
