(2068, 600, 'opis', 'On March 11 this year Hadley Dean, founder of MDC² will be the speaker at <a href=\"https://www.property-forum.eu/forums/conference-property/2021-property-investment-outlook/1186\">2021 Property Investment Outlook</a>.\n\nThis virtual event, prepared by a leading event hun in CEE, Property Forum, will bring together influential investors, bankers and advisors to provide a comprehensive outlook for 2021 on the CEE property investment market.\n\nTogether with a group of top property professionals from the region, Hadley will be covering the topic of “Investment strategies for the second pandemic year”. The panel is taking place at 2:30 pm CET and is available upon registration.'),
