(2245, 1021, 'skrocony_opis', 'We joined forces with the Forest Forever Foundation to build a better world and protect the much-needed forests in Poland.'),
(2246, 1021, 'opis', 'The <a href=\"https://www.lasnazawsze.org.pl/?lang=en\">Forest Forever Foundation</a> has a simple goal that it systematically pursues - it protects forests in Poland. What does it mean? The Foundation takes care of the forests which were previously purchased by the foundation thanks to its donors. The forest areas that are under the care of a team of the foundation and its volunteers will stay with us FOREVER.\n\nMDC<sup>2 </sup> started a cooperation with the Forest Forever Foundation which includes an ongoing support of its operations. As a developer of sustainable warehouse space, the company attaches great importance to ESG, which is the cornerstone of the company\'s activity. In this case, E, but also S plays a key role - while building new projects, we also care for the balance between nature and the effects of human activity.\n\nThe cooperation is long-term and divided into stages, about which we will keep you informed.\n\n<iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/TEi6HVrlXts\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe>\n\n&nbsp;'),
