(2265, 1026, 'skrocony_opis', 'In an interview with Eurologistics (issue 1/2022), Maciej Madejak, CDO and one of the founders of MDC2, talks about the company\'s unique management structure, its approach to ESG strategy, and the future of the warehouse real estate market in Poland.'),
(2266, 1026, 'opis', '\"We pay a lot of attention to the structure in which our people work. Employees should also know how the company works, how it is managed and together determine the next stages of its growth. This is something we wanted to create. from the beginning.\" - said Maciej Madejak.\n\nYou can read the entire interview (available in Polish)  in the latest issue of <a href=\"https://mdc2.pl/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/eurologistics_2022_03_01_przejrzystosa_i_dynamiczny_rozwoj_pdf_bn_k_p.pdf\">Eurologistics.</a>\n\n&nbsp;'),
