(2380, 1113, 'opis', 'It was an honour to be awarded in two out of three Popular Choice categories during the recent <a href=\"https://eurobuildcee.com/en/post/32839-the-glorious-twelfth\">Eurobuild CEE Awards</a>: <strong>Newcomer of the Year and Outstanding Non-Business Achievement of the Year</strong> which recognized our charity association, <a href=\"https://ukrainerelief.pl/\">Ukraine Relief </a>helping Polish families hosting Ukrainian refugees in their homes and supporting Ukrainian children who are aiming to settled down in Poland.\r\n\r\nThe awards were granted to the best the market can offer in 35 categories, in a process that was entrusted to almost 200 judges and independent auditing company KPMG.\r\n\r\nKudos to our team and business partners for everything we achieved in the last 18 months.\r\n\r\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/5jEK3PGMu8c\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),
