(2559, 1356, 'skrocony_opis', 'MDC2 Park Gliwice - forecasted to be the greenest and highest scoring warehouse project in Poland “BREEAM New Construction Outstanding” has concluded a lease of 10,784 sq. m. with one of the world’s leading information technology (IT) companies. MDC² Park Gliwice is located at the intersection of the A4 and A1 motorways in Gliwice, Upper Silesia. MDC2 is the developer. The project is fully financed by Invesco Real Estate, the world\'s leading investor and asset manager of commercial real estate. The advisor in the lease transaction is Colliers.\r\n'),
