(2719, 1462, 'skrocony_opis', 'In a night filled with glitz, glamour, and celebration of excellence in the CEE real estate sector, MDC2 emerged as a shining star at the CEEQA Gala held in Warsaw on May 15, 2024. The company, known for its strong focus on ESG, was honored with the coveted Rising Star of the Year Award, cementing its position as a trailblazer in the industry.'),
(2720, 1462, '_skrocony_opis', 'field_6144f5f47a09c'),
(2721, 1462, 'opis', 'The CEEQA Gala, renowned as the most prestigious annual gathering for real estate professionals in the region, brought together key stakeholders, investors, developers, and industry experts to recognize and applaud outstanding achievements of 2023. Against this backdrop, MDC2\'s triumph in clinching the Rising Star of the Year Award.\n\nThe Rising Star of the Year Award serves as a testament to MDC2\'s outstanding performance, vision, and potential for future growth. The recognition bestowed upon MDC2 at the CEEQA Gala 2024 reaffirms its status as a rising star and underscores the transformative impact of its visionary approach to real estate development.\n\nThe awards are judged by a panel of 36 senior representatives and owners of market leading regional and international companies active in the sector.The annual CEEQA Gala, at which the winners of the awards are announced, is one of the major annual European real estate business events and attracts over 600 industry leaders from more than 50 countries active in the sector, which has led the renewal of the region’s built infrastructure post-communism in what has become one of Europe’s most dynamic real estate markets in recent years experiencing strong market growth.'),
