(4516, 1028, 'opis', 'In 2021, Hadley Dean with other partners established the warehouse development company, MDC<sup>2</sup>. It aims at leading the change in the Polish marketplace by being sustainable, transparent and behaving with integrity. Hadley Dean refers to the ESG, which is a priority for the real estate industry.  Where exactly does he see the need for change on the Polish market?\r\n\r\nWatch the full <a href=\"https://polandweekly.com/2022/03/17/positive-outlook-for-polish-warehouse-market%ef%bf%bc/\">VIDEO INTERVIEW</a> to find out more.'),
