(6540, 1840, 'opis', '<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Dariusz Proniewicz</strong> is a BTS Development Director responsible for sourcing, developing and leasing tailor-made warehouse and logistics projects for specific tenants.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Dariusz has over 18 years of experience in the development of industrial and logistics properties in Poland . During his previous positions at Prologis, Goodman (GLP) and Panattoni he transacted close to 900 000 m<sup>2 </sup>of warehouse space and acquired 300 hectares of land. Notable leasing transactions with Dariusz’s involvement include Action, Knorr-Bremse, Intermarche, Weber, Unilever and Raben.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">He is a graduate of Kraków University of Technology and completed postgraduate studies in Real Estate Valuation at Technical University of Warsaw and Property Appraisal and Management studies at Sheffield Hallam University.</p>'),
