(6646, 1847, 'opis', '<p class=\"v1MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">Magdalena Cieliczko is the Head of Marketing at MDC<sup>2</sup> responsible for communication and marketing activities of the company. She focuses on building the MDC² brand in Poland and strengthening external and internal communication of the business by supporting the management and the development teams. Her tasks include planning and implementing communication goals supporting the business objectives and including coordination of PR activities, digital marketing, events and CSR initiatives.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"v1MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">Magdalena has 25 years of experience in marketing and communications for B2B businesses including real estate, legal and media sectors. She gained her professional experience in companies such as Colliers, EPP, Patpol or New Media Publishing Polska. She graduated from Warsaw University, the faculty of Applied Linguistics.</span></p>'),
