(6843, 1862, 'opis', '<p class=\"v1MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-GB\">MDC<sup>2</sup> Park Łódź South</span></b><span lang=\"EN-GB\"> is a master planned distribution and logistics development with a planned total GLA of 80 000 sq m. MDC<sup>2</sup> Park Łódź South is strategically located in Głuchów, south of Łódź, at the junction of A1 Motorway and the National Roads No. 91 and 12. MDC<sup>2 </sup>Park Łódź South benefits from superb exposure and connectivity.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/dnBqpkJB6BY?si=3NMoE8WaKh-G8Njp\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p class=\"v1MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">Modern businesses require equally modern support. MDC<sup>2</sup> Park Łódź South is a response to the needs of entrepreneurs: logistics and online sales operators, distribution companies who need modern and flexible warehouse space. The owner is <a href=\"https://fortressfund.co.za/\">Fortress REIT Ltd</a>. who also provides a full financing of the project.</span></p>\r\nThe rental offer of any warehouse space is a response to the needs of various entrepreneurs. Each tenant can count on trouble-free contact and maximum adjustment of the offer to their needs. Convenient access from every part of the country, full technological facilities, 24/7 monitoring of the facility and a spacious parking lot are the elements that help scale the business model.'),
(6844, 1862, '_opis', 'field_6142662c0aeff'),
(6845, 1862, 'opis2', 'MDC<sup>2</sup> Park Łódź South is a modern and ecological solution located in central Poland, right next to the A1 motorway south of Łódź. The facility has a total of 80,000 sq. m. of space. The investment is being developed on the basis of the principle of sustainable development and will be certified BREEAM New Construction – Excellent and we strive to make it stand out with:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>PV ready roofs,</li>\r\n 	<li>Chargers for electric cars,</li>\r\n 	<li>Retention reservoirs,</li>\r\n 	<li>Outdoor relaxation zones,</li>\r\n</ul>'),
