(6869, 1862, 'tresci_seo', '<h2>Łódź Warehouses - together into the future!</h2>\r\nMDC<sup>2</sup> Park Łódź South is a response to the ever-growing need to lease large spaces. We create new facilities primarily to meet the needs of users, but also with care for the environment. That is why all distribution centers and warehouse parks under the MDC<sup>2</sup> brand are designed and built taking into account the idea of sustainable construction. This means that all facilities meet stringent ecological standards. MDC<sup>2</sup> industrial properties are distinguished by low emissions of carbon dioxide, exhaust gases and other pollutants. We know that meeting the needs of the present generation is possible without harming future generations.\r\n<h2>Warehouses for rent in Łódź in a convenient location</h2>\r\nMDC<sup>2</sup> Park Łódź South is not only a huge area for any development by the tenant, it also has great access. The convenient location of MDC2 warehouses is as important as providing tenants with full technical facilities. MDC<sup>2</sup> Park Łódź South will be located right next to the A1 motorway, thanks to which access from various parts of Poland, and above all from Łódź and its vicinity, will be trouble-free. The idea of sustainable construction is as important as relationships with people – that’s why MDC<sup>2</sup> means not only modern usable areas, but also a friendly working environment and professional customer service. Every interested person and tenant can count on professional and quick help, as well as the maximum adjustment of the offer to their needs.\r\n<h2>Modern warehouse for rent Łódź.</h2>\r\nMDC<sup>2</sup> Łódź South is not only convenient access and modern infrastructure with full back-up facilities. It also provides modern solutions in every other respect. Trouble-free and pleasant contact, sensitivity and openness to individual needs – all this is a guarantee of satisfaction and peace in running your business on a daily basis. You can focus on what’s most important and let us handle the rest. Peace and safety, convenient location and easy access, all with the benefit of our planet in mind.'),
