(6911, 1863, 'tresci_seo', '<h2>A modern warehouse for rent</h2>\r\nProgress can go hand in hand with environmental protection - MDC² Park Gliwice is one of the examples of this and on how to achieve it with relative ease. Thanks to the parks’s design, we can put into use another state of the art and innovative facility. Perfect location, extensive infrastructure with all amenities and minimal interference in the natural environment - these are the most important advantages of this warehouse park. Thanks to a flexible approach to customers, anyone interested in renting warehouse space will receive an offer tailored to their needs. As a result, the warehouse space in Gliwice will satisfy every type of tenant.\r\n<h2>Ecological warehouses for rent - Gliwice</h2>\r\nMDC² Park Gliwice is another MDC2 project which, while meeting the high demands of modern society, does not work to the detriment of future generations. Green buildings, designed in accordance with the concept of sustainable development, are the future not only for sales, distribution and logistics, but also for entire societies. Thanks to low emissions of carbon dioxide and exhaust gases, as well as low electricity consumption, this warehouse in Silesia helps protect nature.\r\n\r\nAt the same time the extensive infrastructure includes all amenities, making the daily use of warehouse space a pure pleasure.\r\n<h2>Warehouse rental in Gliwice</h2>\r\nMDC² Park Gliwice is a proposition for everyone: small and large entrepreneurs. Competent staff - always ready to help, provide information, solve a problem and adjust the offer to the tenant\'s needs. Ecological solutions, modern infrastructure, great location and convenient access - all at a competitive price - are the greatest advantages of MDC2 Park Gliwice.\r\n\r\nMDC² is not only space for rent - it is also people. We know how important it is to feel good in your workplace, so we make every effort to create favorable conditions for it. On a daily basis, we also educate employees and contractors in the essence and implementation of modern, ecological solutions, with future generations in mind.'),
