(7410, 1912, 'opis', 'Konrad Gąsiorowski is responsible for the construction management of warehouse projects developed by MDC2. He has 15 years of professional experience gained working both on developer and general contractor sides. His portfolio include over 250,000 m2 of industrial BTS buildings delivered for the companies such as Ontex, Knorr Bremse, Action, Danfoss, Scania, as well as speculative multitenant warehouse buildings. Prior to joining MDC2, Konrad worked as Senior Project Manager in Panattoni and Dekpol SA.\r\n\r\nHe is a Civil Engineer having unlimited building license for managing of construction and the graduate of the Warsaw University of Technology as well as Military University of Technology.'),
