(7422, 1913, 'opis', '<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-GB\">Elżbieta Koncewicz </span></b><span lang=\"EN-GB\">is a Construction Coordinator at MDC² and works within the Operations and Construction team. </span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Her role is to manage and support the work of the team including maintaining the proper flow of information and documentation as far as construction processes are concerned. Elżbieta gained her professional experience in warehouse development companies, Panattoni and Goodman Poland, where she was essential in coordinating information circulation and supporting in execution of tenants\' projects as well as providing an administrative support. Elżbieta studies at the Warsaw School of Economics - Finance and Accounting faculty. She speaks fluent Belarussian, Russian and English.</span></p>'),
